Package org.sat4j.tools

Interface SolutionFoundListener

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ILauncherMode
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CheckMUSSolutionListener
    public interface SolutionFoundListener
    Allows the end user to react when a new solution is found. This is typically the case when doing some upper bound optimization, or iterating on the models, or computing all MUses.
    Since:
    2.3.3
    Author:
    leberre
